title: Catherine - Hot Saki & Bedtime Stories
description:
Hot Saki and Bedtime Stories is the fourth and final studio album by the alternative rock band Catherine. It was released in 1996. D'arcy Wretzky, drummer Kerry Brown's wife at the time, contributed vocals on this record. "Four Leaf Clover" was a single from this album.
